require(xml2)
library(tidyverse)
library(berryFunctions)
library(rvest)




theme_set(theme_classic())

  doc <- read_xml("Untitled-2.svg") %>% xml_ns_strip()
  lines <- xml_nodes(doc, 'line')
  
  linesdf <-
    tibble(bind_rows(lapply(xml_attrs(lines), as.data.frame.list))) %>% mutate_at(c("x1", 'x2', 'y1', 'y2'), as.character) %>% mutate_at(c("x1", 'x2', 'y1', 'y2'), as.numeric) %>% mutate(y1 =-y1, y2 = -y2) %>% mutate(length = sqrt((x2 - x1) ^ 2 + (y2 - y1) ^ 2))
  

  
ggplot(linesdf,aes(x=x1,xend=x2,y=y1,yend=y2,color=class))+geom_segment()


black_lines = linesdf %>% filter(class=="st14") %>% mutate(horizontal = abs(y2-y1)<10*abs(x2-x1)   ) %>% mutate(vertical = !horizontal)



ggplot(black_lines,aes(x=x1,xend=x2,y=y1,yend=y2,color=horizontal))+geom_segment()


ggplot(black_lines, aes(x=length))+geom_histogram()


ticks = black_lines %>% mutate(is_tick=length<30) %>%filter(is_tick)
horiz_limits =  ticks %>% filter(horizontal) %>% filter(y1==max(y1)| y1==min(y1))
vert_limits =  ticks %>% filter(vertical) %>% filter(x1==max(x1)| x1==min(x1))


ggplot(bind_rows(horiz_limits,vert_limits),aes(x=x1,xend=x2,y=y1,yend=y2,color=horizontal))+geom_segment()


x_min_real = ymd("2020-04-26")
x_max_real= ymd("2020-10-11")
y_min_real = 10
y_max_real = 40

x_min_svg = min(vert_limits$x1)
x_max_svg= max(vert_limits$x1)
y_min_svg = min(horiz_limits$y1)
y_max_svg = max(horiz_limits$y1)
